IAdminFinanceService ..> WithdrawalHistoryItem
AdminFinanceService ..> WithdrawalHistoryItem
AdminFinanceRepository ..> PlatformWithdrawal
IStripeConnectService ..> StripeWithdrawalResponseDto
AdminFinanceService ..> StripeWithdrawalResponseDto

